		<td width="150" align="left" valign="top" class="row2"><span class="name"><a name="83636"></a><b>Balanz son of Anz</b></span><br /><span class="postdetails">Wielder of the BanHammer of Oppression<br /><br /><br />Joined: 30 Nov 2000<br />Posts: 1194<br /></span><br /></td>
		<td class="row2" width="100%" height="28" valign="top"><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
			<tr>
				<td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=83636&amp;sid=fa8498249091bd9824bfdf6c2237f866#83636"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Sun Sep 07, 2003 11:23 pm<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: </span></td>
				<td valign="top" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=83636&amp;sid=fa8498249091bd9824bfdf6c2237f866"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>   </td>
