This is incorrect, due to the pervasive idea that the "taunt" button is a fixed aggro gain, like the inverse of concussion, which is not the case.
<br />

<br />
The way I understand it, Taunt (as an ability) takes the aggro value of the highest item on the list, and adds Your difference from that, plus 1.
